{"tid":559128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10跨黨派英議員 撐提名雙學三子角逐諾獎","createTime":"2018-02-13T02:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T03:22:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ab7b52d5aa69c5f07cb8f6909877ff1bf29bb8","tid":559128,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"早前美國跨黨派參議員提名黃之鋒、羅冠聰和周永康角逐諾貝爾和平獎，10位英國國會議員也表態支持今次的提名，並提出動議以示支持。<br />\n<br />\n身兼英國國會議員的保守黨人權委員會主席Fiona Bruce向國會提出動議，支持今次的提名，指認同三子作為雨傘運動的領袖，以和平方式捍衛基本自由和民主，守護《中英聯合聲明》所保障的香港高度自治。此項動議已集結英國跨黨派支持，包括工黨、蘇格蘭民族黨、保守黨、民主聯盟黨。<br />\n<br />\n動議字眼如下：「英國國會歡迎黃之鋒、羅冠聰、周永康和雨傘運動獲提名為2018年的諾貝爾和平獎，以認同他們以和平方式捍衛民主」。提出動議的保守黨人權委員會主席Fiona Bruce說，「雨傘運動是世界上最和平和最克制的示威之一，由傑出的年輕領袖領導，他們爭取自由和民主值得我們全力支持，我希望諾貝爾和平獎委員會嚴肅考慮今次提名。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180213/57826085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180213%2F57826085&d=2WMtyAVBEoU6qmllr5eBaAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=ce9f2c02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180213%2F57826085&h=37ed4673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180213/57826085</a>"},{"pid":"c8d87483244e749fc9e06137b4cf2bdc431dee6d","tid":559128,"uid":38973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:29:55.000Z","msg":"hear, hear"},{"pid":"c0595e5fa8df7bc85e5ade468a55eb440d0b9570","tid":559128,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img1.momoshop.com.tw/goodsimg/0004/262/738/4262738_B.jpg?t=1507237322\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.momoshop.com.tw%2Fgoodsimg%2F0004%2F262%2F738%2F4262738_B.jpg%3Ft%3D1507237322&h=1b84a0f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a222aadfb84ea26c7642ffb1dceb4cab0dff756","tid":559128,"uid":35870,"like":